INetworkReachableNodesCommandImp Class Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

FdoINetworkReachableNodesCommand subclasses from FdoINetworkCommand and is the interface that defines the FDO network reachable nodes analysis feature. An instance can be created through the FdoIConnection::CreateCommand method. Not all FDO providers will support this command. The FdoICommandCapability should be used to verify if a given provider support this command.

Note: This Help topic is provided for informational use only. There is no interface or support provided. Autodesk reserves the right to change the software related to the content herein.
